task.summary: Refactored labels into separate package and class
Changed layout setup from deprecated VBoxBuilder to constructor that pulls from LayoutSettings
moved menu stuff into new class
Added a bunch of stub classes
moved editors and ignoreNextPress to State
renamed State to Store and CurrentState to State, to make code more concise and readable
made createNew use enum instead of text
moved new editor logic to VFile. should be easier to read and understand now
View -> Web Page now previews the current file(if it's an html file)
made Editor store a reference to its container tab. added Editor.select() as a replacement for State.x.tabs.getSelectModel().select()
created VFile.load() method to remove choosing/loading files from Main
fixed bug where opening a file also created a new one
properly cited tutorial code to avoid plagiarism
made editor extend TextArea for simplicity
fixed indicateFileModified() to avoid using getEditorForTextArea()
changed Controller.run() to allow returning futures
added callbacks and placeholders to Controller.run()
